channel.title: No one is aloud on?
channel.description: This is quite a puzzle I'm having.. I have a laptop, I used to host my own server. But then my Wireless Network got screwed and I had to make another one. Now, when I turn on my server it lets no one on except me when I use the default 127.0.0.1. I triple checked everything, got a new java update and updated all my RSPS related things. Someone please help me.

item.title: No one is aloud on?
item.dc:creator: @XxJtxX XxJtxX
item.description:
@XxJtxX wrote:

[quote=“tonypker13, post:9, topic:247247”]If people cannot log on, and you are the only one, you portforwarded incorrectly.
You can’t argue back on that. Try port forwarding again.[/quote]
I just tried port forwarding for the fourth time and still nothing happened.
